OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1993FTonight's edition of Have I Got
OL,7,FNews for You saw Roy Hattersley
OL,8,Freplaced by a tub of lard.
OL,9,
OL,10,FMr Hattersley failed to turn up for the
OL,11,Fprogramme recording. This was
OL,12,Fapparently the third time he had
OL,13,Fcancelled at the last minute.
OL,14,
OL,15,FThe tub of lard was credited at the end
OL,16,Fof the programme: "The Rt. Hon. Tub of
OL,17,FLard MP".
